<div id="main">
  <h1 id="title">Erwin Boyones</h1>
  <div>The Self Made Billionaire</div>
  <div id="img-div">
    <img id="image" src="https://scontent.fceb1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/1184905_532429876830642_1388720401_n.jpg?_nc_cat=0&oh=befa02ecb0a717cb6ee15410af21b2d7&oe=5BC69046" alt "pic from flickr">
    <div id="img-caption">
      Engr. Erwin V. Boyones, the one seeing flying off the screen from the picture taken somewhere back in 2010.
    </div>
  </div>
  <div id="tribute-info">
    <ul>
      <h3 id="headline">Here's an initial time line of Engr. Erwin Boyones' life:</h3>
      <li><strong>1988</strong> - Born in Pagsabungan, Mandaue City Cebu</li>
      <li><strong>2000</strong> - Finishes elementary education at Casate Elementary School of Ubay Bohol</li>
      <li><strong>March 2004</strong> - Finishes high school education at Pagsabungan National High School of Pagsabungan Mandaue City Cebu</li>
      <li><strong>June 2005 to December 2005</strong> - Short stint as newspaper salesman for various local newspaper publication of Cebu i.e Super Balita, Banat News, SunStar, Cebu Daily News & The Freeman</li>
      <li><strong>2006 - 2007</strong> - Works as utility in one of Cebu's auto dealer company. Also at this time around, he started to train Wushu and became part of Wushu Cebu team to compete in the national competions. Which he did twice.</li>
      <li><strong>2008</strong> - Got a short stint as cartridge ink refiller at inke then later absorbed by the then Tills n Labels now Abztrak Inc.</li>
      <li><strong>2009</strong> - Started Baccalaureate Degree in Electronics Engineering at University of San Jose - Recoletos Cebu. Still continues to work at Abztrak Inc.</li>
    </ul>
    <blockquote>
      <p>"My life is a constant struggle as most of life is, but I will not back down from any challenges that I`ll met along the way"</p>
      <div>-- Erwin Boyones</div>
    </blockquote>
